Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:18.49,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}还不如直接做出来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:23.16,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}“幸运点数”给我一大桶Please
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:29.62,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}心儿软绵绵  感觉暖洋洋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:33.17,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想把这感觉分享给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:36.92,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}才不会无聊无聊无聊  一起来做各种各样的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.51,0:22:42.39,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}像兔子一样飞跳起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.05,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}飞跳起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:48.06,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}连明天也要追赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:49.73,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一定要追赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:55.94,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}令人心跳的巧克力脆皮甜点♪  在嘴里发出悦耳的清脆酥响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:23:00.95,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悠悠哉哉  虽然轻松的话题根本说不完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:04.99,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}闪闪发光地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.08,0:23:06.62,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}舞动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.66,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\fs18\pos(416,330)}Pirouette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:10.66,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在树荫透过的日光下跳着回旋舞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.21,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}转来转去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:18.13,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一瞬间握住你的手  让脚步声响彻街头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:25.93,EDCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}可爱  美味  同一个时间  和你在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------TXT----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  完全沉迷于芭蕾舞之中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是自然而然就跳起芭蕾的程度了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打醉拳啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天看到电视上播放的电影里有醉拳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种借口就像是麻耶一样诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿着花束的高中生有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天高中好像是毕业典礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  我的志愿到底怎么选才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.93,0:00:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到了不得不去考虑它的时候了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起毕业典礼  心爱她…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.55,0:01:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没有毕业吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能不能升学啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你在担心那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得学姐没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是说一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不像是没问题的样子？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在毕业典礼的时候感动得不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到我们了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且我一想到我自从来到这个小镇已经快一年了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光阴似箭呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  看到了果然在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么哭起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们约好了要碰头的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝点茶庆祝升学什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到了家很棒的咖啡馆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃你们要不要一起来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们出轨到其他的店了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要从兔子之家毕业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座无虚席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和高中生组的座位分开来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想像她们那样变成熟些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对后辈自然地说出「一起来喝茶吧」的邀请什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能自然地邀请别人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么惠  要不要试试看？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小姐你很可爱呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  一  一起来喝茶吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是可疑的搭讪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱路学姐喝茶的姿势好像大小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种大人的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成为那样的高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.61,TXTH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16}饮料（仅限无酒精饮料）  免费一杯券
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:05:00.61,TXTH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs16}只要用一张本券便可以兑换自选饮料一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张券还可以使用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费券是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无破绽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好憧憬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么有种妹妹会被人抢走的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有成熟一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点更优雅了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是您的下午茶套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我并没有点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是那边的客人为您点的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可不是酒吧啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是姐姐我为了可爱的妹妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲手献上的礼物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说  吃这个的时候是有着先后顺序的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从三明治开始吃起吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是从司康饼开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说如果不能优雅地吃掉这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法成为成熟的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只要模仿纱路她们就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在吃热狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也点了一样的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是模仿的好机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感受到有羡慕的视线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能正在被观察着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观察？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在确认我们是否为值得尊敬的学姐呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…我明白了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想通了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位！我所说的关于相对论的解释清楚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在展示自己头脑聪明！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比较狭义相对论和广义相对论的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是更喜欢狭义点的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然接上话茬了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就算现在要背诵波若心经什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连纱路也？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}果然  广义和狭义的比起来  概念有点太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狭义相对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过好像在享用之前需要先聊会天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要说些大人的话题呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前第一次拿哥哥跑腿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}买东西的话把JUMP买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可称不上是大人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下  下次去酒吧时间的兔子之家坐坐看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好成熟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便彻夜长谈怎么样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我可不会允许那种事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被听到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是下午茶时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道怎么吃这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的吃法不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的就好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山小姐所说的普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们的普通可不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  难道说我并不普通吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃她们正在和青山小姐聊天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是很重要的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在向青山小姐咨询意见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我已经观察过她们了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不过她们可并不值得尊敬呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山小姐  下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被智乃她们拜托来观察你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相…相对论吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狭义和广义…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色…色即是空…空…空即是色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我比较喜欢宇宙弦理论哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是稀奇啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  大家也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是巧合呢…我也…喜欢宇宙的弦理论…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不知道下午茶套餐的吃法所以在观察我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模仿行动的时候不知不觉就跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用把它想成什么郑重的东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  想要成为成熟的女性的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候只要开心地吃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为礼仪本身就是能让大家都开心而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教官的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深刻铭记于我心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  他们回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:10:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有空的位置  我们就把桌子拼起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来通过抽签随机排座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能作弊把自己跟学妹们坐在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很公平的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够和大家一起开茶会就已经很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也尝一尝这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  啊这个也尝尝看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为离她们离得最远就沮丧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好远…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我有想问的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都能问哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狭义相对论和广义相对论有什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你们要显摆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还得要再加把油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多问我先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那你打算怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作…作为姐姐要更加…好好有所成长才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  我来替你拎包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用对姐姐客气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有对你客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那我来背你走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  咦  不要客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐寄来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的回信好快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱  已经早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是春假  但是也不能睡懒觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身人偶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早餐要凉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和平时不一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是早餐烧焦了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完早餐之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会好好教教你狭义相对论和广义相对论的区别的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱的样子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起平时来说动作更敏捷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  这是在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抚摸提比的动作也很敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您光临
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招待客人的动作也很敏捷！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来带您去座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是绅士呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(363.2,324)}牛郎店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被看作是另一种店的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刘海的方向和平时的完全相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.97,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软绵绵  软绵绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软绵绵的天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本尊的话一定会忍不住抱上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认真工作的话是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么不过感觉很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到打击了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望心爱不要努力过度而发烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一语中的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做到这个份上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…会来哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说两者有什么关联吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让姐姐看到你努力的样子对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得必须要振作点来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为智乃的姐姐有在好好以身作则什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱的姐姐很严格吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  她很温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然上面还有两个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她对他们说教的样子好帅气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说教…调教师吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调教…我…我难道会比现在被管教得更严吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.98,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}呜呜不要不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕到发抖了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以憧憬着姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来做妹妹的也有不少苦衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我来帮你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现出你好的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过作为独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很羡慕你有那么多兄弟姐妹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理世…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把理世作为我的妹妹来介绍的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…和智乃一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为普通的朋友就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐修行？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样才能看起来很能干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想给姐姐看看我成长的一面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让从刚才开始就一直怕得发抖的智乃镇定下来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}调教师…会被摸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我在啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}别  别这样  不要这样嘛  好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是同样的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这差距怎么就这么大呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果理世她们犯点迷糊什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来是不是就会显得心爱很能干呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逆向思维
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…既然我都已经说过要帮忙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我想下单…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分不清楚咖啡的区别…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱  快来救场！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我数学很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心买进了一吨重的咖啡罐头…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面包可以用火焰喷射器来烤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩这样根本让人看不下去嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可都是为了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就让我们来锻炼心爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱  这里可还留着灰尘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好像觉醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆模式…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把这个飞盘捡回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}看好了  要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是为了什么的特训啊
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.09,0:17:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.46,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想变得像姐姐那样
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望你们来当我妹妹
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大家一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  人家想吃面包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}来帮我写作业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…算…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这得持续到什么时候为止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到心爱察觉到这并没有什么意义为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天谢谢大家帮我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一点拿铁咖啡  不成敬意…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  是心爱画的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起刚开始的时候  有很大进步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们一直都在看着所以没有察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就是有在好好成长的证明嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直帅呆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那我现在就给你们画个更厉害的东西好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看3D的拿铁拉花！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算作为店员有所成长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作为姐姐来说还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3D拿铁拉花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是提比吧喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱啊…真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管过多久都是不靠谱的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得心爱是一个好姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算嘴上说着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好展现出好的态度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱只是因为姐姐要来就有点慌张过度了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不要太在意就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明最近心爱在的时候很开心来着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纱路  你在担心心爱和智乃她们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得心爱应该对自己更有点自信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  纱路也应该对自己自信点才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然把话题转到我身上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人家有点担心纱路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要担心人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时隔一年的重逢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是让人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅有期待  也有不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个心爱很罕见地在烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为姐姐的成长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是个不知天高地厚的烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然同为一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事情可不是勉强自己而是好好传达才行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶尔也会说出些有道理的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有个不知天高地厚的儿子在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她差不多应该到车站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去接她真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信里好像写着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我自己会来店里的  想看看心爱工作时的样子」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吧？  心爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…咦咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱因为过于紧张而蓝屏了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快去接客啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信里不是写着要你好好工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂  心爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心爱的…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:40.57,TXTI,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frx12\fry8\pos(322.4,107.6)\frz317.3}变成兔子的咖啡师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是不妙的状况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体来说是怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…估计会变得很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.09,0:23:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是指不妙的部分
